text: The following highways are numbered 653: ==United States== * 20px Nevada State Route 653, an east–west state highway in Washoe County, Nevada, serving the city of Reno * 20px Pennsylvania Route 653, a 26-mile-long (42 km) state highway in Fayette and Somerset counties in Pennsylvania, United States * 20px Puerto Rico Highway 653, an east-west highway in Arecibo and Hatillo municipalities in Puerto Rico * 20px Virginia State Route 653, a secondary route in Virginia
title: List of highways numbered 653
